label: Charles Fraser Sketchbook, 1793-1796, Mechanical Drawing
description: Two drawings in brown ink labelled profile and front; on left 6 feet 1 inch on side, 7 feet 4 inches on top, 2 ft 6 inches down right, 2 ft 4 inches inside. On right: 6 ft 6 inches on left, 5 ft on bottom, 1/p. at right base. At lower right in larger hand: 90 feet 4 in. by 4 - and 12 ft 6 by 6-; above [Scautling?]. 4 pieces...7 ft 4 i.; 4 .... 6 ft 6.; 6..(?)....5 ft.; beam + Warp 5 ft. 8 I.; 2 pieces 2 ft. 8 I. [possibly for rice cultivation?]
